data.title: Show Your Skills With OBSS Code Masters!
data.meta_description: Show Your Skills With OBSS Code Masters!
data.text:
Show your coding and algorithm skills at the Code Master Contest, which will take place on Wednesday, February 28, as part of the Career Festival '18.

The competition was organized by the Career Development Office in collaboration with OBSS. The prizes for the winner will be an Iphone X and a money award for the runner up.

While the first stage of the competition will take place individually within the campus, the first 3 ranking students will include 2 other members to form a team in the second stage and be entitled to participate in the competition between universities at the OBSS Technopark Office on April 29-30.

**The competition is open to 3rd and 4th year students from the Computer Engineering, Information Systems and Technologies, and Management Information Systems Departments.

For application please visit: http://bit.ly/2A8trHv

Competition Date: February 28th Wednesday Time: 17.00

Competition Location: Engineering Building Laboratory B410

For more information: obss.com.tr/academic

Note: Students who will participate in the competition will be exempt from their classes at competition time via a coupon.

For further questions:kariyerdestek@yeditepe.edu.tr

Telephone: 0216 578 00 00 - 3254
